708111f-a.text:
(1)
Third Ave., west side, south from East 65th to 64th Streets, showing prominently a 4-story structure, No. 1108 Third Ave. (also 160 East
65th Street) at the S.W. corner.
June 12, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
A detail of same, showing Nos. 1108 to 1100. Overhead is the
Third Ave. Elevated Line.
June 12, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
